ng%20fear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Florida%20teachers'%20union%20says%20Gov.%20Ron%20DeSantis'%20administration%20is%20using%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremist%20agenda%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bcensor%26quot%3B%20AP%20Psychology%20after%20the%20College%20Board%20said%20the%20course%20was%20%26quot%3Beffectively%20banned%26quot%3B%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-desantis-expansion-of-dont-say-gay-to-all-grades-2023-3%5C%22%3Estate's%20parental%20rights%20law%20critics%20have%20called%20%26quot%3BDon't%20Say%20Gay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGov.%20DeSantis%20continues%20to%20use%20every%20possible%20tactic%20to%20stoke%20fears%20among%20parents%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20dividing%20and%20distracting%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Spar%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Florida%20Education%20Association%20%E2%80%94%20the%20largest%20labor%20union%20in%20the%20Southeast%20representing%20over%20150%2C000%20education%20workers%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website%20%E2%80%94%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20College%20Board%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20group%20that%20manages%20AP%20coursework%20at%20high%20schools%20across%20the%20US%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20Thursday%20that%20the%20Florida%20Department%20of%20Education%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.collegeboard.org%2Fstatement-ap-psychology-and-florida%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Beffectively%20banned%20AP%20Psychology%20in%20the%20state%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20telling%20superintendents%20that%20it%20is%20illegal%20for%20courses%20to%20discuss%20sexual%20orientation%20and%20gender%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20College%20Board%20said%20that%20its%20AP%20Psych%20course%20asks%20students%20to%20%26quot%3Bdescribe%20how%20sex%20and%20gender%20influence%20socialization%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20development%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20topics%20it%20said%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20curriculum%20for%2030%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20under%20DeSantis'%20law%2C%20teachers%20are%20prohibited%20from%20discussing%20gender%20identity%20and%20sexual%20orientation%20in%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20College%20Board%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20that%20Florida%20told%20school%20districts%20that%20they%20can%20only%20teach%20the%20course%20if%20they%20remove%20%26quot%3Bany%20mention%20of%20these%20essential%20topics.%26quot%3B%20The%20board%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20that%20it%20refuses%20to%20modify%20or%20censor%20its%20college-level%20standards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20College%20Board's%20announcement%2C%20Spar%20said%20DeSantis%20%26quot%3Band%20his%20handpicked%20bureaucrats%20are%20interfering%20in%20the%20right%20of%20parents%20to%20decide%20what%20is%20best%20for%20their%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20attempt%20to%20censor%20the%20AP%20Psychology%20course%20is%20just%20one%20more%20example%20of%20the%20governor's%20extremist%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20Spar%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20big%20takeaway%20here%20is%20that%20our%20students%20are%20losing%20out%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20one%20man's%20political%20ambitions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Florida%20Department%20of%20Education%20said%20that%20the%20course%20wasn't%20banned%2C%20telling%20Insider%20that%20it%20remains%20listed%20in%20the%20course%20code%20directory%20for%20the%202023-24%20school%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20encourage%20the%20College%20Board%20to%20stop%20playing%20games%20with%20Florida%20students%20and%20continue%20to%20offer%20the%20course%20and%20allow%20teachers%20to%20operate%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20other%20advanced%20course%20providers%20(including%20the%20International%20Baccalaureate%20program)%20had%20no%20issue%20providing%20the%20college%20credit%20psychology%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20clarification%20on%20if%20the%20law%20prohibits%20the%20course%20from%20including%20a%20curriculum%20on%20gender%20and%20sexuality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20College%20Board%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20that%20any%20AP%20Psychology%20course%20taught%20in%20Florida%20%26quot%3Bwill%20violate%20either%20Florida%20law%26quot%3B%20by%20including%20essential%20topics%20related%20to%20gender%20and%20sexuality%2C%20or%20violate%20%26quot%3Bcollege%20requirements%26quot%3B%20by%20not%20including%20such%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EColin%20Sharkey%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20another%20teachers'%20group%2C%20the%20Association%20of%20American%20Educators%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3Bunclear%20language%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binaccurate%20interpretation%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20law%20%26quot%3Bcreates%20a%20chilling%20effect%20on%20educators%20that%20may%20go%20well%20beyond%20the%20intent%20of%20the%20lawmakers%20and%20disrupt%20the%20learning%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-teachers-union-ap-psych-course-criticizes-desantis-administration-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691181807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cd5b78f5d4870019e224ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-teachers-union-ap-psych-course-criticizes-desantis-administration-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teachers'%20union%20accused%20DeSantis%20of%20using%20%26quot%3Bevery%20possible%20tactic%20to%20stoke%20fears%20among%20parents%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20dividing%20and%20distracting%20us.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ggoodwin%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Eliza%20Goodwin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fflorida-teachers-union-ap