sinsider.com%2Fwhats-next-2023%5C%22%3EWhat's%20Next%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20where%20we%20ask%20CEOs%20of%20prominent%20companies%20across%20industries%20about%20how%20rapidly%20evolving%20trends%20influence%20their%20approach%20to%20leadership.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20is%20becoming%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20commodities%20on%20Wall%20Street%2C%20and%20the%20social-investing%20fintech%20eToro%20is%20betting%20on%20the%20tech%20to%20improve%20internal%20processes%20and%20customer-facing%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20ChatGPT's%20splashy%20debut%20in%20November%202022%2C%20generative%20AI%20has%20captured%20people's%20and%20corporations'%20imaginations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20is%20a%20subset%20of%20AI%20designed%20to%20ingest%20copious%20amounts%20of%20information%20and%20create%20new%20content.%20The%20underlying%20models%2C%20called%20large%20language%20models%2C%20can%20form%20something%20new%20from%20written%20prompts.%20Generative%20AI%20has%20created%20things%20as%20diverse%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-script-succession-finale-screenwriter-wga-reaction-amid-strike-2023-5%5C%22%3Escreenplays%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchat-gpt-recipe-vegan-food-blogger-nisha-vora-how-to-2023-4%5C%22%3Erecipes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdating-ai-chatbot-replika-artificial-intelligence-best-thing-to-happen-2023-2%5C%22%3Eromantic%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinance%2C%20an%20industry%20that%20runs%20on%20data%2C%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-chatgpt-could-be-used-on-wall-street-investing-dealmaking-2023-2%5C%22%3Eexploring%20ways%20to%20leverage%20generative%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fetoro-investing-review%5C%22%3Eretail-investing%20fintech%20eToro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20work%20is%20underway%20to%20see%20how%20generative%20AI%20can%20be%20deployed%20to%20employees%20and%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%20having%2032%20million%20registered%20users%20and%203%20million%20account%20holders%20globally%20means%20you%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20data.%20And%20as%20you%20know%2C%20AI%20is%20a%20hungry%20beast%20that%20needs%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Lule%20Demmissie%2C%20eToro's%20US%20CEO%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20a%20natural%20thing%20for%20us%20to%20evolve%20our%20intellectual%20property%20that%20really%20runs%20our%20Copy%20investor%20program%20to%20also%20have%20AI%20as%20part%20of%20its%20DNA.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemmissie%20was%20referring%20to%20CopyTrader%2C%20eToro's%20product%20designed%20to%20let%20users%20see%20other%20people's%20positions%20in%20a%20social-media-like%20feed%20with%20the%20option%20to%20track%20and%20replicate%20an%20individual's%20investing%20strategies.%20The%20company%20declined%20to%20disclose%20how%20many%20investors%20use%20CopyTrader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fintech%20said%20it%20was%20experimenting%20with%20adding%20generative%20AI%20so%20users%20could%20slice%20and%20dice%20the%20information%20in%20the%20social%20feed%20more%20deeply%20and%20creatively%2C%20such%20as%20asking%20to%20combine%20two%20users'%20portfolios%20or%20seeing%20how%20many%20users%20have%20large%20positions%20in%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EeToro%20is%20looking%20at%20generative%20AI%20to%20speed%20up%20some%20employees'%20workflows%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EeToro%20says%20employees%20can%20expect%20to%20benefit%20from%20generative%20AI%20as%20well%3A%20The%20fintech's%20looking%20at%20ways%20to%20deploy%20generative%20AI%20in%20its%20marketing%20and%20compliance%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20marketing%2C%20eToro%20is%20testing%20using%20AI%20to%20translate%20written%20content%20into%20different%20languages.%20Demmissie%20said%20that%20because%20the%20company%20operates%20in%20100%20markets%2C%20translating%20marketing%20materials%20is%20%26quot%3Bincredibly%20expensive%20and%20complicated%20when%20you%20do%20that%20on%20a%20manual%20basis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20compliance%2C%20eToro%20is%20exploring%20ways%20to%20present%20certain%20disclosures%20in%20a%20fun%20or%20interesting%20way.%20Demmissie%20said%20the%20fintech%20had%20fed%20%26quot%3Bvery%20serious%26quot%3B%20disclosures%20subject%20to%20Financial%20Industry%20Regulatory%20Authority%20rules%20into%20ChatGPT%20and%20asked%20the%20AI%20to%20make%20the%20disclosures%20sound%20Shakespearean%20or%20like%20a%20professor%20while%20adhering%20to%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDisclosures%20are%20boring%20and%20dry%2C%20and%20they're%20important%20for%20users%20to%20actually%20understand%2C%20so%20if%20you%20have%20this%20fun%20and%20interesting%20way%20of%20actually%20communicating%20these%20things%2C%20it%20could%20be%20an%20effective%20way%20to%20make%20sure%20people%20pay%20attention%2C%26quot%3B%20Demmissie%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20that%20while%20it%20hadn't%20turned%20these%20use%20cases%20into%20products%2C%20it%20was%20evaluating%20which%20generative-AI%20applications%20to%20pursue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EUsing%20generative%20AI%20with%20guardrails%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20company%20thinks%20about%20opportunities%20that%20come%20with%20generative%20AI%2C%20it%20can't%20ignore%20the%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemmissie%20said%20that%20opening%20up%20to%20generative%20AI%20may%20take%20a%20mindset%20shift%2C%20adding%20that%20because%20the%20tech%20%26quot%3Bis%20essentially%20starting%20to%20think%20on%20its%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20mitigating%20risks%20would%20be%20more%20about%20setting%20up%20guardrails%20than%20controlling%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemmissie%20said%20she%20was%20also%20aware%20of%20the%20models'%20shortfalls%20and%20biases%20and%20the%20moral%20hazards%20of%20dealing%20with%20those.%20For%20instanc