0sometimes%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20houses%20can%20be%20found%20listed%20in%20%26quot%3Bakiya%20banks%2C%26quot%3B%20pages%20operated%20by%20local%20governments%20as%20part%20of%20a%20program%20launched%20by%20Japan's%20Ministry%20of%20Land%2C%20Infrastructure%2C%20Transport%20and%20Tourism%20(MLIT).%20The%20Japanese%20government%20estimated%20in%202018%20that%20there%20were%20nearly%208.5%20million%20abandoned%20homes%20in%20the%20country.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.akiyabanks.com%2Fabout-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAkiyabanks.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20website%20with%20information%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Japanese%2C%20provides%20a%20collective%20directory%20of%20all%20known%20municipal%20akiya%20banks%20in%20Japan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20incentives%20and%20low%20prices%20have%20attracted%20some%20Japanese%20urbanites%20looking%20for%20a%20change%20of%20pace%2C%20and%20have%20also%20increasingly%20attracted%20the%20attention%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fjapanese-government-selling-rural-homes-cheap-akiya-banks-2021-5%5C%22%3Eforeign%20buyers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJaya%20Thursfield%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Chihiro%2C%20moved%20from%20London%20to%20Japan%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fabandoned-house-renovation-japan-diy-before-after-photos-2021-8%5C%22%3Ebuying%20an%20abandoned%20Japanese%20farmhouse%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ibaraki%2C%20a%20Japanese%20prefecture%20about%20an%20hour's%20drive%20northeast%20from%20Tokyo.%20The%20couple%20said%20they%20bought%20their%20house%20for%20around%20%2430%2C000%20at%20auction%20in%202019%20and%20have%20spent%20about%20%24150%2C000%20on%20extensive%20renovations%2C%20documenting%20the%20process%20of%20turning%20it%20into%20their%20dream%20home%20on%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FTokyoLlama%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20cleaned%20out%20the%20previous%20owner's%20belongings%2C%20which%20included%20two%20cars%2C%20a%20tractor%2C%20and%20farm%20equipment%2C%20redid%20all%20the%20plumbing%20and%20electrical%20wiring%2C%20installed%20new%20flooring%20across%20the%20house%2C%20and%20completely%20renovated%20the%20kitchen%20and%20bathrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221272%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Thursfields'%20kitchen%20when%20they%20first%20bought%20the%20abandoned%20house.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cc01870b651c00193a3c3d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22704%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Thursfields'%20kitchen%20needed%20a%20complete%20renovation%2C%20but%20first%20it%20had%20to%20be%20cleaned%20out.%3Cp%3EJaya%20Thursfield%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExtensive%20cleaning%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fold-houses-for-sale-japan-akiya-prices-fixer-upper-2023-4%5C%22%3Erenovations%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20necessary%20to%20make%20an%20akiya%20livable.%20Many%20older%20akiya%20are%20considered%20structurally%20fragile%20according%20to%20the%20Building%20Standard%20Law%20in%20Japan%2C%20which%20was%20first%20introduced%20in%201950%2C%20and%20has%20since%20been%20amended%20to%20improve%20the%20sturdiness%20of%20older%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20many%20Japanese%20buyers%20preferring%20newly%20built%20houses%2C%20some%20homes%20are%20demolished%20after%20only%2020-30%20years.%20And%20while%20houses%20in%20the%20US%20typically%20appreciate%20in%20value%2C%20houses%20in%20Japan%20tend%20to%20gradually%20depreciate%20in%20value%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Koo%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20at%20Japan's%20Nomura%20Research%20Institute%2C%20previously%20told%20Insider%20that%20in%20Japan%2C%20once%20a%20home%20is%20more%20than%2010%20or%2015%20years%20old%2C%20its%20value%20is%20%26quot%3Bworse%20than%20nothing%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20demolishing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLand%20without%20anything%20on%20it%20has%20a%20higher%20value%20than%20land%20with%20a%20pre-owned%20house%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Koo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBethany%20Nakamura%20moved%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-japan-abandoned-home-homeownership-cultural-shift-2023-7%3Fmrfhud%3Dtrue%5C%22%3EUS%20to%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20teach%20English%20in%202021.%20In%202022%2C%20she%20found%20an%20opportunity%20to%20live%20in%20an%20akiya%20for%20free%2C%20only%20paying%20utilities.%20Although%20the%20house%20was%20in%20good%20condition%2C%20she%20said%20she%20chose%20not%20to%20buy%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20don't%20think%20that%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20for%20foreign%20people%20to%20jump%20into%20homeownership%20in%20the%20Japanese%20countryside%20right%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Nakamura%20previously%20told%20Insider%20for%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20about%20her%20experience.%20%26quot%3BMoving%20from%20America%20to%20Japan%20presents%20a%20very%20different%20culture.%20It's%20a%20different%20real-estate%20market.%20People%20may%20not%20know%20right%20away%20if%20it's%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20the%20long%20term.%20And%20once%20you%20own%20a%20home%2C%20it's%20very%20difficult%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20costs%20of%20these%20houses%20create%20buzz%2C%20but%20Nakamura%20said%20that%20it's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20step%20towards%20financial%20freedom%20or%20long-term%20stability%2C%20and%20that%20cultural%20differences%20can%20be%20difficult%20to%20adapt%20to.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20might%20take%20two%20or%20three%20years%20for%20someone%20to%20really%20have%20a%20solid%20understanding%20of%20how%20they%20interact%20in%20the%20community%2C%20what%20their%20expectations%20are%2C%20and%20how%20the%20community%20will%20react%20when%20they%20do%20things%20that%20they%20don't%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-abandoned-home-in-japan-what-to-know-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691173953000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64cc028b0f3dff001956a89e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-abandoned-home-in-japan-what-to-know-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Government%20subsidies%20and%20low%20costs%20are%20attracting%20foreigners%2C%20but%20buyers%20should%20be%20aware%20of%20potential%20renovation%20costs%20and%20uncertain%20resale%20values.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kkirschner%40insider.com%20(Kylie%20Kirschner%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuy-abandoned-home-in-japan-what-to-know-2023-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%229%20yesteryear%20actresses%20you%20must%20follow%20on%20Insta%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691173800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102425069%2Cimgsize-57200.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2F9-yesteryear-bollywood-actresses-you-must-follow-on-instagram%2Fphotostory%2F102425069.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102425069.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8B9%20yesteryear%20Bollywood%20actresses%20you%20must%20follow%20on%20Instagram%E2%80%8B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2F9-yesteryear-bollywood-actresses-you-must-follow-on-inst