ilm%2Fnews%2Fandrea-iervolino-tuscany-film-studios-1235688100%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fandrea-iervolino-tuscany-film-studios-1235688100%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karnataka%20Minister%20Praises%20Delhi's%20Mohalla%20Clinics%2C%20Then%20Does%20A%20U-Turn%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20praising%20the%20AAP%20government's%20Mohalla%20Clinic%20initiative%2C%20Karnataka%20Health%20Minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20on%20Friday%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Boverhyped%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20was%20left%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%26quot%3B%20after%20a%20visit%20to%20one%20such%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20alleged%20that%20Mr%20Rao%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20after%20praising%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20initiative%20and%20thereafter%20changed%20his%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rao%20alone%20can%20clarify%20why%20his%20statement%20changed%20from%20praising%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20to%20criticising%20it%2C%20the%20AAP%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bunfortunate%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20and%20the%20AAP%20are%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20visited%20an%20'Aam%20Aadmi%20Mohalla%20Clinic'%20at%20Panchsheel%20Park%20in%20Delhi.%20He%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Karnataka%20Bhavan%20medical%20officer%20Karthik%2C%20according%20to%20an%20official%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20four%20hours%20after%20praising%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20initiative%2C%20Gundu%20Rao%20made%20a%20U-turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVisited%20a%20mohalla%20clinic%20in%20Delhi%20with%20hardly%20any%20people%20there.%20Our%20clinics%20in%20Karnataka%20have%20more%20facilities%2C%20including%20a%20laboratory%2C%20to%20do%20immediate%20tests%20for%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress%20leader%20tweeted.%20%26quot%3BI%20guess%20it%20is%20overhyped%20and%20I%20came%20back%20feeling%20disappointed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20visit%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20minister%20saw%20the%20facilities%20at%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20welfare%20of%20staffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Panchsheel%20Park%20mohalla%20clinic%2C%20Mr%20Rao%20had%20praised%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20model%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20functioning%20%26quot%3Bvery%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20heard%20a%20lot%20about%20mohalla%20clinics%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20see%20them%20personally.%20I%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20how%20they%20(AAP%20government)%20are%20implementing%20the%20health%20policies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20southern%20states%20such%20as%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20health%20has%20always%20been%20a%20priority.%20Every%20state%20has%20got%20something%20good%20that%20we%20can%20learn%20from.%20We%20have%20something%20similar%20(to%20mohalla%20clinics)...%20we%20have%20'namma%20clinics'.%20We%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20we%20can%20improve%20our%20system.%20I%20saw%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20and%20it%20is%20functioning%20very%20well%20People%20are%20also%20appreciating%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20said%20the%20comparison%20between%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20and%20namma%20clinic%20is%20%26quot%3Bunjust%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20received%20a%20phone%20call.%20Following%20the%20call%2C%20he%20mentioned%20an%20important%20meeting%20and%20left%20the%20location.%20A%20while%20later%2C%20he%20tweeted%20criticising%20the%20mohalla%20clinic.%20However%2C%20only%20Dinesh%20Rao%20can%20clarify%20why%20his%20statement%20changed%20from%20praising%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20to%20criticising%20it%20after%20the%20phone%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20his%20tweet%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20Namma%20Clinic%20in%20Karnataka%20had%20better%20infrastructure%20than%20Mohalla%20Clinic.%20To%20verify%20this%20claim%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Karnataka%20team%20visited%20a%20Namma%20Clinic%20in%20his%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20found%20that%20both%20Namma%20Clinic%20and%20Primary%20Health%20Centre%20were%20located%20adjacent%20to%20each%20other.%20People%20mentioned%20that%20the%20Primary%20Health%20Centre%20had%20been%20closed%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Namma%20Clinic%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20is%20just%20a%20name.%20It%20was%20initiated%20by%20the%20BJP%20government.%20The%20clinic%20provides%20only%20primary%20treatment%20for%20some%20illnesses%20like%20fever.%20Patients%20are%20referred%20to%20other%20hospitals...%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comparison%20between%20Namma%20Clinic%20and%20Delhi's%20Mohalla%20Clinic%20is%20unjust%2C%20the%20AAP%20said%2C%20adding%20mohalla%20clinics%20are%20well-equipped%20and%20treatment%20is%20provided%20free%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20claim%20made%20by%20Rao%20that%20Namma%20Clinic's%20infrastructure%20is%20superior%20to%20Mohalla%20Clinic%20is%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B.%20Namma%20Clinic%20lacks%20good%20facilities%2C%20it%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government's%20mohalla%20clinic%20is%20a%20neighbourhood%20facility%20for%20providing%20free%20primary%20healthcare%20to%20residents.%20The%20mohalla%20clinic%20programme%20is%20among%20the%20flagship%20initiatives%20of%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%20to%20boost%20the%20primary%20healthcare%20system%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20interaction%20with%20reporters%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Panchsheel%20Park%20mohalla%20clinic%2C%20the%20Congress%20minister%20was%20also%20asked%20whether%20this%20visit%20was%20planned%20since%20they%20are%20allies%20now%2C%20to%20which%20he%20said%20this%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bdepartment%26quot%3B%20matter%20and%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%26quot%3B%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlliance%20is%20a%20different%20issue%20and%20a%20political%20one.%20We%20will%20go%20to%20other%20states.%20Rajasthan%20has%20a%20health%20policy.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20BJP%20state%20also%20(where%20we%20can%20visit).%20That%20is%20the%20concept%20of%20federalism%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20BJP-led%20Centre%2C%20he%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bis%20creating%20a%20situation%20where%20this%20approach%20of%20working%20together%20is%20getting%20lost%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20look%20at%20opposition-ruled%20states%20as%20enemies.%20Politically%20they%20give%20trouble%20and%20they%20even%20trouble%20the%20state%20governments.%20The%20(services)%20ordinance%20is%20overruling%20people's%20issues.%20If%20you%20weaken%20an%20elected%20government%20it%20weakens%20democracy.%20Exchange%20of%20views%20is%20something%20that%20is%20good%20and%20should%20be%20done%20always.%20I%20have%20also%20extended%20invitation%20to%20Delhi%20health%20minister%20to%20see%20what%20is%20being%20done%20on%20various%20fronts%20(in%20Karnataka)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bharadwaj%20said%20his%20Karnataka%20counterpart%20told%20him%20about%20how%20good%20the%20hospitals%20are%20in%20the%20southern%20state.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20also%20visit%20his%20state.%20All%20states%20should%20learn%20from%20each%20other.%20I%20am%20very%20happy%20that%20they%20have%20come%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20quote-tweeting%20Mr%20Bharadwaj's%20tweets%20on%20Gundu%20Rao's%20visit%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20said%20Delhi%20will%20learn%20from%20the%20good%20work%20done%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKarnataka%20health%20minister%20visits%20Delhi%20mohalla%20clinics.%20We%20welcome%20him%20and%20his%20team.%20We%20all%20have%20to%20learn%20from%20each%20other.%20Delhi%20will%20also%20learn%20from%20the%20good%20work%20done%20by%20Karnataka%20govt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%20500%20mohalla%20clinics%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20that%20offer%20free%20primary%20healthcare%20services%20to%20patients%2C%20including%20212%20different%20types%20of%20medical%20tests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691173260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fc34h37pg_dinesh-gundu-rao-mohalla-clinic-twitter_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-health-minister-first-praises-delhis-mohalla-clinic-initiative-then-calls-it-overhyped-4270643%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20alleged%20that%20Dinesh%20Gundu%20Rao%20received%20a%20phone%20call%20after%20praising%20the%20mohalla%20clinic%20initiative%20and%20thereafter%20changed%20his%20stance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-health-minister-first-praises-delhis-mohalla-clinic-initiative-then-calls-it-overhyped-4270643%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-health-minister-first-praises-delhis-mohalla-clinic-initiative-then-calls-it-overhyped-4270643%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkarnataka-health-minister-first-praises-delhis-mohalla-clinic-initiative-then-calls-it-overhyped-4270643%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%201%2C000-year-old%20system%20of%20irrigation%20channels%20could%20help%20protect%20Spain%20from%20extreme%20heat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222202%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Border%20Collie%20called%20walks%20on%20a%20cracked%20riverbed%20due%20to%20the%20drought%20in%20July%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c95fb0048ff200190f50c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221646%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20dog%20walks%20on%20a%20cracked%20riverbed%20due%20to%20the%20drought%20in%20July%202023.%3Cp%3EJORGE%20GUERRERO%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAn%20ancient%20Moorish%20invention%20could%20protect%20Spain%20from%20a%20future%20of%20severe%20droughts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20irrigation%20channels%20run%20through%2015%2C000%20miles%20of%20Spain's%20mountainous%20provinces.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAs%20generational%20knowledge%20dwindles%2C%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20know%20how%20these%20channels%20operate%20continues%20to%20decline.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F19%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fspain-drought-acequias.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C000-year-old%20Moorish%20invention%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20the%20answer%20to%20Spain's%20increasing%20heat%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20chain%20of%20over%2015%2C000%20miles%20of%20acequias%20throughout%20the%20mountainous%20region%20of%20Spain%20is%20being%20restored%20as%20a%20low-cost%20way%20to%20bring%20water%20to%20crops%20during%20a%20time%20of%20increasing%20heat%20and%20droughts.%20Acequias%20are%20a%20network%20of%20irrigation%20canals%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Moors%20that%20bring%20snowmelt%20down%20from%20the%20mountains%20and%20distribute%20it%20to%20the%20land%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20believe%20that%20the%20ancient%20solution%20will%20help%20spread%20water%20throughout%20the%20arid%20region%20of%20Spain%20and%20maintain%20agrarian%20practices.%20The%20only%20problem%20is%20that%20few%20people%20know%20how%20acequias%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Spain%20moved%20toward%20an%20agricultural%20model%20that%20emphasized%20reservoirs%20and%20many%20in%20rural%20communities%20in%20Spain%20moved%20to%20cities%2C%20knowledge%20of%20the%20acequias%20system%20dwindled.%20Only%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20in%20these%20communities%20know%20how%20to%20restore%20the%20acequias.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorians%20and%20conservationists%20are%20working%20together%20to%20restore%20these%20systems%20and%20build%20back%20the%20generational%20knowledge%20required%20to%20operate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20acequias%2C%20from%20the%20Arabic%20word%20%26quot%3Bas-saqiya%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20water%20conduit%20%E2%80%94%20were%20built%20by%20the%20Moors%20between%20the%20eighth%20and%2010th%20centuries%20in%20what%20was%20then%20known%20as%20the%20Al-Andalus%20region%20of%20the%20Iberian%20Peninsula.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20view%20of%20the%20Alhambra%20Palace%20in%20Granada%2C%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c94ceb048ff200190f35d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20view%20of%20the%20Alhambra%20Palace%20in%20Granada%2C%20Spain.%3Cp%3EBerk%20Ozkan%2FAnadolu%20Agency%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20acequias%20was%20an%20elegant%20solution%20of%20moving%20water%20that%20transformed%20the%20entire%20landscape%20of%20the%20mountainous%20region.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221647%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20various%20crops%20in%20the%20Andalusian%20area%20of%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c94d82cf0778001968c8c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221235%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20aerial%20view%20of%20the%20various%20crops%20in%20the%20Andalusian%20area%20of%20Spain.%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Archive%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESpain's%20Andalusia%20region%20has%20a%20Mediterranean%20climate%20with%20long%20summers%20and%20dry%20winters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Moors%20introduced%20the%20acequias%20to%20Spain%20and%20used%20it%20to%20move%20water%20more%20effectively%20through%20the%20mountains%2C%20they%20changed%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fenvironment%2F2022%2Fapr%2F11%2Fancient-water-system-restore-spain-sierra-nevada-aoe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elandscape%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%20the%20Andalusian%20provinces%2C%20Granada%20and%20Almeria%2C%20are%20the%20leading%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Ftopics%2F7595%2Fagriculture-sector-in-spain%2F%23topicOverview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagricultural%20regions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Spain.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20acequias%20take%20water%20from%20snowmelt%20and%20precipitation%20up%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20mountains%20of%20Spain.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Landscape%20of%20Sierra%20Nevada%20Mountains%20in%20the%20High%20Alpujarras%2C%20near%20Capileira%2C%20Granada%20Province%2C%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c95d29048ff200190f4d1c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELandscape%20of%20Sierra%20Nevada%20Mountains%20in%20the%20High%20Alpujarras%2C%20near%20Capileira%2C%20Granada%20Province%2C%20Spain.%3Cp%3EGeography%20Photos%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBy%20diverting%20the%20water%20into%20these%20constructed%20pathways%2C%20the%20snowmelt%20is%20able%20to%20slow%20down%20and%20replenish%20more%20of%20the%20land%20along%20the%20way.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Landscape%20of