The%20trailer%20for%20the%20film%20has%20just%20been%20released%20(below).%20The%20film%20screens%20on%20Aug.%2014%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Heart%20of%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Leo%20Barraclough%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fbody-lightdox-sarajevo-1235687922%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fbody-lightdox-sarajevo-1235687922%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fbody-lightdox-sarajevo-1235687922%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Defining%20Hate%20Speech%20%5C%22Complex%5C%22%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Flags%20%5C%22Free%20Speech%5C%22%20Concern%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDefining%20hate%20speech%20is%20complex%20but%20the%20real%20problem%20in%20tackling%20them%20lies%20in%20the%20implementation%20and%20execution%20of%20law%20and%20judicial%20pronouncements%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20days%20after%20parts%20of%20Haryana%20were%20rattled%20by%20communal%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20and%20SVN%20Bhatti%2C%20which%20was%20hearing%20a%20plea%20against%20the%20rallies%20to%20be%20organised%20by%20right-wing%20outfits%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20region%20over%20the%20communal%20clashes%20in%20Haryana%20along%20with%20other%20petitions%20against%20hate%20speeches%2C%20asked%20about%20whether%20the%20events%20were%20peaceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20CU%20Singh%2C%20appearing%20for%20petitioner%20Shaheen%20Abdullah%2C%20said%20hate%20speeches%20were%20made%20at%20the%20rallies%20but%20no%20violence%20was%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20told%20Mr%20Singh%20that%20a%20solution%20to%20hate%20speeches%20can%20be%20found%20through%20collective%20efforts%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20don't%20you%20sit%20together%20and%20try%20to%20find%20a%20solution%3F%20You%20see%2C%20the%20definition%20of%20hate%20speech%20is%20fairly%20complex%20and%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20ensured%20that%20it%20does%20not%20transverse%20into%20the%20area%20of%20free%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20my%202020%20judgement%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Amish%20Devgan%20versus%20Union%20of%20India%20which%20deals%20with%20balancing%20of%20competing%20interests%20of%20free%20speech%20and%20the%20need%20to%20prevent%20the%20spread%20of%20hatred%20and%20communal%20disharmony.%20There%20are%20several%20other%20verdicts%20of%20the%20top%20court.%20You%20see%20the%20main%20problem%20is%20implementation%20and%20execution%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Khanna%20told%20Singh%20and%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20who%20represented%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20said%20the%20top%20court%20has%20specified%20what%20hate%20speech%20is%20in%20the%202018%20verdict%20in%20the%20Tehseen%20Poonawalla%20case%20and%20no%20one%20can%20justify%20hate%20speech%20against%20any%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20law%20is%20very%20clear%20that%20if%20any%20hate%20speech%20is%20made%2C%20one%20can%20lodge%20an%20FIR%20and%2C%20if%20FIR%20is%20not%20registered%2C%20then%20one%20can%20approach%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20Mehta%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20said%20some%20individuals%20and%20organisations%20were%20now%20approaching%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directly%20instead%20of%20the%20police%20station%20concerned%20with%20complaints%20about%20hate%20speeches%20and%20seeking%20contempt%20action%20by%20the%20top%20court%20over%20violation%20of%20its%20orders.%20Also%2C%20he%20said%2C%20a%20new%20practice%20has%20emerged%20where%20people%20approach%20the%20court%20voicing%20apprehension%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20hate%20speeches%20being%20made%20at%20an%20event%20and%20seeking%20advance%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMehta%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20April%2028%20order%20of%20the%20top%20court%20that%20directed%20all%20states%20and%20union%20territories(UTs)%20to%20register%20cases%20against%20those%20making%20hate%20speeches%20even%20without%20any%20complaint%2C%20terming%20these%20speeches%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20offence%26quot%3B%20capable%20of%20affecting%20the%20secular%20fabric%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExtending%20the%20scope%20of%20its%202022%20order%20beyond%20three%20states--Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20to%20authorities%20that%20any%20hesitation%20to%20act%20against%20hate%20speeches%20will%20be%20viewed%20as%20contempt%20of%20the%20top%20court%20and%20appropriate%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20the%20erring%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20there%20should%20be%20a%20mechanism%20so%20that%20no%20one%20has%20to%20come%20to%20the%20top%20court%20time%20and%20again.%20Social%20tension%20is%20in%20nobody's%20interest%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20will%20have%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20as%20there%20has%20to%20be%20some%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20hate%20speeches.%20Everybody%20should%20not%20be%20coming%20to%20court%20and%20there%20should%20be%20some%20mechanism.%20We%20have%20thought%20of%20something%20and%20we%20will%20let%20you%20all%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20and%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20a%20resumed%20hearing%20after%20two%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20said%20he%20has%20also%20received%20some%20video%20clips%20of%20hate%20speeches%20and%20the%20petitioner%20should%20be%20directed%20to%20amend%20his%20petition%20because%20he%20is%20selectively%20targeting%20only%20one%20community%20and%20ignoring%20the%20hate%20speeches%20made%20by%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%202%2C%20with%20communal%20clashes%20claiming%20six%20lives%20in%20parts%20of%20Haryana%20close%20to%20Delhi%2C%20the%20top%20court%20had%20ordered%20enhanced%20deployment%20of%20security%20personnel%20in%20sensitive%20areas%20and%20a%20crackdown%20on%20hate%20speech%20but%20refused%20to%20stop%20the%20proposed%20rallies%20by%20VHP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20in%20the%20NCR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%20last%20year%2C%20the%20top%20court%20directed%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Uttarakhand%20to%20crack%20down%20hard%20on%20those%20making%20hate%20speeches%2C%20calling%20them%20shocking%20for%20a%20country%20that%20is%20religion-neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20that%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20envisages%20a%20secular%20nation%2C%20the%20court%20had%20directed%20the%20three%20states%20to%20promptly%20register%20criminal%20cases%20against%20the%20offenders%20without%20waiting%20for%20a%20complaint%20to%20be%20filed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691167380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F4qgfvaco_supreme-court-new_625x300_11_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefining-hate-speech-fairly-complex-supreme-court-flags-free-speech-concern-4269631%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defining%20hate%20speech%20is%20complex%20but%20the%20real%20problem%20in%20tackling%20them%20lies%20in%20the%20implementation%20and%20execution%20of%20law%20and%20judicial%20pronouncements%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20days%20after%20parts%20of%20Haryana%20were%20rattled%20by%20communal%20violence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefining-hate-speech-fairly-complex-supreme-court-flags-free-speech-concern-4269631%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefining-hate-speech-fairly-complex-supreme-court-flags-free-speech-concern-4269631%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdefining-hate-speech-fairly-complex-supreme-court-flags-free