3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%20100%20Crore%20Per%20Acre%20Is%20New%20Record%20For%20Telangana%20Land%20Prices%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20plot%20near%20Hyderabad%20sold%20for%20a%20whopping%20Rs%20100%20crore%20per%20acre%20at%20an%20online%20auction%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20record%20for%20land%20prices%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20highest%20bid%20for%20the%203.6-acre%20plot%20in%20Kokapet%20was%20Rs%20362%20crore%2C%20made%20by%20Rajapushpa%20Properties%20Private%20Limited%20for%20Happi%20Heights%20Neopolis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20auction%20of%20the%20seven%20land%20parcels%20spanning%2045.33%20acres%20at%20Neopolis%20layout%20raised%20Rs%203%2C320%20crore%20for%20Hyderabad%20Metropolitan%20Development%20Authority.%20The%20average%20bid%20was%20Rs%2073.23%20crore%20per%20acre%20and%20the%20lowest%20being%20Rs%2067.25%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20highest%20bid%20did%20not%20cross%20Rs%2060%20crore%20during%20Phase-I%20of%20the%20Neopolis%20auction%20in%20July%202021%20when%2049%20acres%20were%20sold.%20The%20average%20was%20around%20Rs%2040%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArvind%20Kumar%2C%20Telangana's%20special%20chief%20secretary%20for%20Urban%20Infrastructure%20and%20Development%2C%20said%20the%20land%20rates%20have%20risen%20due%20to%20multiple%20factors%20like%20state-of-the-art%20infrastructure%20and%20greenfield%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B36%20and%2045-metre%20roads%20are%20actually%20unheard%20of.%20Then%20there%20is%20a%20dedicated%20240%20KV%20substation%20and%20seamless%20connectivity%20to%20Outer%20Ring%20Road%20trumpet%20junction%2C%20a%20clear%20title%20and%20strategic%20location%2C%20since%20it%20is%20adjacent%20to%20ORR%2C%20just%2030%20minutes%20from%20Hyderabad's%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Kumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20land%20parcels%20are%20meant%20for%20high%20rise%20buildings%20with%20unlimited%20Floor%20Space%20Index%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20steep%20rise%20in%20land%20prices%20can%20threaten%20the%20city's%20attractiveness%20as%20an%20affordable%20real%20estate%20market%20as%20there%20is%20always%20competition%20with%20cities%20like%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20differed%20with%20this%20view%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20price%20discovery%20by%20the%20market.%20With%20the%20residential%20sector%20already%20bullish%2C%20the%20rates%20fit%20into%20the%20prevailing%20rates%2C%20with%20average%20at%20Rs%2073%20crore%20per%20acre.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20by%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Neopolis%20layout%20sale%2C%20the%20government%20has%20announced%20another%20greenfield%20workstation%20at%20Budwel.%20The%20registrations%20are%20now%20open%20for%2014%20plots%20spanning%20100%20acres%2C%20to%20be%20auctioned%20on%20August%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20includes%20three%20plots%20of%20less%20than%20five%20acres%2C%20nine%20plots%20of%20up%20to%20eight%20acres%20and%20two%20plots%20over%2010%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691161260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F1rbpvl48_neopolis-layout-hyderabad-_625x300_04_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhyderabad-news%2Frs-100-crore-per-acre-is-new-record-for-telangana-land-prices-4270185%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20plot%20near%20Hyderabad%20sold%20for%20a%20whopping%20Rs%20100%20crore%20per%20acre%20at%20an%20online%20auction%2C%20setting%20a%20new%20record%20for%20land%20prices%20in%20Telangana.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhyderabad-news%2Frs-100-crore-per-acre-is-new-record-for-telangana-land-prices-4270185%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fhyderabad-news%2Frs-100-crore-per-acre-is-new-record-for-telangana-land-prices-4270185%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22amp