dra%20Singh%20Dhoni's%2015-year-long%20international%20career%20saw%20him%20rise%20through%20the%20ranks%20as%20an%20unorthodox%20wicket-keeper%20batsman%20to%20one%20of%20Indian%20cricket's%20all-time%20greats.%20He's%20the%20most%20successful%20captain%20the%20country%20has%20seen%20and%20a%20revered%20figure%20in%20international%20cricket%20as%20%26quot%3BCaptain%20Cool.%26quot%3B%20Everyone%20has%20to%20start%20somewhere%20and%20former%20India%20cricketer%20Syed%20Saba%20Karim%20revealed%20one%20such%20instance%20in%20the%20commentary%20box%2C%20about%20the%20emergence%20of%20Dhoni%2C%20before%20his%20call-up%20to%20the%20national%20team.%20Karim%20recalled%20the%20first%20time%20he%20met%20Dhoni%20and%20how%20he%20became%20familiar%20with%20his%20skillsets%20after%20becoming%20a%20selector%20for%20Bihar%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20story%20is%20very%20interesting.%20The%20first%20time%20I%20saw%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20it%20was%20his%20second%20year%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%20He%20used%20to%20play%20for%20Bihar.%20I%20saw%20him%20batting%20and%20keeping%2C%20and%20I%20still%20remember%20while%20he%20was%20batting%2C%20he%20had%20that%20brilliance%20which%20we%20even%20saw%20later%2C%20playing%20big%20lofted%20shots%20to%20a%20spinner%20or%20a%20pace%20bowler.%20Even%20for%20wicket-keeping%2C%20the%20footwork%20that%20one%20should%20have%20was%20lacking%20a%20bit.%20We%20worked%20with%20him%20on%20this%20at%20that%20time%2C%20and%20he%20still%20remembered%20what%20he%20was%20taught%20then.%20When%20we%20used%20to%20chat%2C%20he%20used%20to%20speak%20about%20it.%20It%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20MS's%20career%20where%20he%20actually%20got%20going.%20In%20one-dayers%2C%20we%20started%20to%20let%20him%20open%20because%20his%20batting%20was%20so%20strong%20and%20he%20used%20to%20get%20quick%20runs%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Saba%20Karim%20on%20JioCinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarim%20then%20discussed%20Dhoni's%20first%20series%20for%20India%20%E2%80%98A'%20where%20his%20batting%20performances%20convinced%20the%20national%20team%20selectors%20to%20finally%20give%20him%20a%20chance.%20The%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20second%20turning%20point%20was%20the%20tri-series%20in%20Kenya%20between%20India%20%E2%80%98A'%2C%20Pakistan%20%E2%80%98A'%2C%20and%20Kenya.%20MS%20Dhoni%20got%20an%20opportunity%20to%20play%20because%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20was%20joining%20the%20national%20team.%20There%2C%20MS%20kept%20the%20wickets%20well%20and%20for%20batting%20don't%20even%20ask!%20We%20played%20against%20Pak%20%E2%80%98A'%20twice%20and%20he%20batted%20so%20well%20in%20the%20series.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20there%20it%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20his%20career%20and%20after%20that%2C%20his%20name%20was%20in%20the%20reckoning.%20I%20even%20remember%20I%20was%20in%20Calcutta%20at%20that%20time%2C%20and%20Sourav%20(Ganguly)%20was%20the%20captain.%20I%20went%20to%20meet%20him%20and%20I%20told%20him%20there%20is%20this%20keeper%20who%20should%20come%20into%20the%20Indian%20team%20because%20he%20was%20batting%20so%20well%20and%20was%20such%20a%20safe%20keeper.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Sourav%20hadn't%20seen%20MS%20play%20just%20before%20we%20toured%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20he%20wasn't%20selected%20for%20that%20tour.%20But%20he%20was%20after%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691158500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F0ugl060g_ms-dhoni-innings-_625x300_07_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fex-bcci-selector-reveals-the-one-surprising-turning-point-in-ms-dhonis-career-that-got-him-going-4269863%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20India%20cricketer%20recalled%20the%20first%20time%20he%20met%20MS%20Dhoni%20and%20how%20he%20became%20familiar%20with%20his%20skillsets%20after%20becoming%20a%20selector%20for%20Bihar%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%