%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274565%2Flibrarian-grows-vegetable-fruits-flowers-on-terrace-gardening-facebook%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarious%20Facebook%20campaigns%3C%2Fa%3E%20urging%20people%20to%20come%20join%20us%20with%20their%20bottles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20advertised%20it%20in%20a%20way%20that%20caught%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20%E2%80%94%20we%20asked%20them%20to%20come%20with%20their%20bottles%20and%20that%20we%20would%20convert%20the%20bottles%20into%20whatever%20piece%20they%20fancied.%20This%20gave%20a%20boost%20to%20our%20business%2C%20and%20by%20word%20of%20mouth%2C%20we%20started%20getting%20flooded%20with%20orders%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20products%20are%20priced%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%20300%20and%20Rs%201%2C600.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20did%20not%20have%20any%20formal%20training%20in%20working%20with%20glass%2C%20so%20they%20had%20their%20fair%20share%20of%20mistakes.%20%E2%80%9CGlass%20breaks%20very%20easily%20and%20we%20have%20to%20be%20quite%20careful%20with%20it.%20We%20used%20the%20internet%20and%20hired%20some%20glass%20artists%20to%20help%20us%20with%20the%20process.%20We%20have%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20hits%20and%20misses%2C%20but%20it%20is%20practice%20alone%20that%20has%20helped%20us%20come%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Madhuri.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Madhuri%20collects%20bottles%20from%20customers%20and%20ragpickers%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fkavi-2-1691153952-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.