to%20effect%20which%20will%20be%20notified%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20in%20a%20tweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EQ%3A%20Why%20has%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGoI_MeitY%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40GoI_MeitY%3C%2Fa%3E%20finalized%20new%20norms%20for%20import%20of%20IT%20hardware%20like%20Laptops%2C%20Servers%20etc%3F%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAns%3A%20There%20will%20be%20a%20transition%20period%20for%20this%20to%20be%20put%20into%20effect%20which%20will%20be%20notified%20soon.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnPls%20read%20%F0%9F%91%87%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fu5436EA0IG%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fu5436EA0IG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40Rajeev_GoI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRajeev_GoI%2Fstatus%2F1687429148875051010%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clarification%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20the%20government%20announced%20the%20curbs%20and%20said%20they%20will%20be%20implemented%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20imposed%20a%20licensing%20requirement%20for%20the%20import%20of%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20personal%20computers%20to%20help%20promote%20domestic%20manufacturing%20of%20these%20products%20under%20the%20production-linked%20incentive%20(PLI)%20scheme%20for%20IT%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20curbs%20will%20also%20help%20curtail%20the%20import%20of%20these%20goods%20from%20China%20and%20Korea%2C%20reported%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20government%20official%2C%20speaking%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20said%20there%20are%20several%20reasons%20behind%20the%20imposition%20of%20these%20restrictions%2C%20the%20primary%20being%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20that%20the%20security%20of%20our%20citizens%20is%20fully%20safeguarded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%2C%20once%20imposed%2C%20will%20make%20it%20mandatory%20for%20companies%20planning%20to%20bring%20laptops%20and%20computers%20for%20sale%20in%20India%20to%20seek%20permission%20or%20license%20from%20the%20government%20for%20their%20inbound%20shipments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Directorate%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20(DGFT)%20issued%20the%20notification%2C%20which%20said%20that%20the%20restrictions%20will%20be%20imposed%20under%20HSN%20Code%208471%20on%20seven%20categories%20of%20electronic%20gadgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691154960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-04%2Flaptop-generic-reuters-650_650x400_71428936324.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-laptop-import-ban-not-effective-immediately-government-gives-transition-period-4269578%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Restrictions%20on%20the%20import%20of%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20all-in-one%20personal%20computers%2C%20and%20ultra-small%20computers%20and%20servers%20will%20not%20be%20imposed%20immediately%20and%20there%20will%20be%20a%20transition%20period%20to%20implement%20them%2C%20the%20centre%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-laptop-import-ban-not-effective-immediately-government-gives-transition-period-4269578%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-laptop-import-ban-not-effective-immediately-government-gives-transition-period-4269578%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-laptop-import-ban-not-effective-immediately-government-gives-transition-period-4269578%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20Stays%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Conviction%20in%20Defamation%20Case%2C%20Questions%20Lower%20Court%20on%20Sentence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21120741%2FUntitled-design-2-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20(August%204)%20stayed%20the%20conviction%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20a%20defamation%20case%20against%20him.%20A%20Surat%20court%20had%20earlier%20found%20him%20guilty%20and%20handed%20him%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years%E2%80%99%20imprisonment%20%E2%80%93%20leading%20to%20his%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20Gujarat%20high%20court%20had%20refused%20to%20stay%20the%20conviction%2C%20after%20which%20Gandhi%20had%20appealed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20staying%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20conviction%2C%20his%20disqualification%20also%20now%20stands%20in%20abeyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20order%20questioned%20the%20sentence%20handed%20to%20Gandhi%20by%20the%20lower%20court.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justices%20B.R.%20Gavai%2C%20P.S.%20Narasimha%20and%20P.V.%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20said%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20the%20trial%20court%20did%20not%20give%20specific%20reasons%20for%20imposing%20the%20maximum%20punishment%20under%20the%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-congress-leader-rahul-gandhi-conviction-stay-criminal-defamation-case-modi-thieves-remark-234384%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20quoted%20the%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sentence%20for%20an%20offence%20punishable%20under%20Section%20499%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20is%20maximum%20of%20two%20years%20of%20sentence%20or%20fine%20or%20both.%20The%20learned%20trial%20judge%2C%20in%20the%20order%20passed%20by%20him%2C%20has%20awarded%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years.%20Except%20the%20admonition%20to%20the%20petitioner%20by%20this%20Court%20in%20a%20contempt%20proceeding%2C%20no%20other%20reason%20has%20been%20granted%20by%20the%20learned%20trial%20judge%20while%20imposing%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20it%20is%20only%20on%20account%20of%20the%20maximum%20sentence%20of%20two%20years%20imposed%20by%20the%20learned%20trial%20judge%20that%20the%20provisions%20of%20Section%208(3)%20of%20the%20Representation%20of%20Peoples%20Act%20came%20into%20play.%20Had%20the%20sentence%20been%20a%20day%20lesser%2C%20then%20the%20provisions%20would%20not%20have%20attracted.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EParticularly%20when%20the%20offence%20was%20non-compoundable%2C%20bailable%20and%20cognizable%2C%20the%20least%20which%20was%20expected%20from%20the%20learned%20trial%20judge%20was%20to%20give%20reasons%20for%20imposing%20the%20maximum%20punishment.%20Though%20the%20learned%20appellate%20court%20and%20the%20High%20Court%20have%20spent%20voluminous%20pages%20in%20rejecting%20the%20applications%2C%20these%20aspects%20are%20not%20seen%20considered.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20however%2C%20also%20said%20that%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20in%20Kolar%20before%20the%202019%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20for%20which%20the%20case%20was%20filed%20%E2%80%93%20were%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20in%20good%20taste%E2%80%9D.%20Gandhi%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20question.%20Why%20do%20all%20these%20thieves%20have%C2%A0Modi%C2%A0in%20their%20names%20whether%20it%20is%20Nirav%C2%A0Modi%2C%20Lalit%C2%A0Modi%C2%A0or%20Narendra%C2%A0Modi%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20how%20many%20more%20such%20Modis%20will%20come%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Purnesh%20Modi%20had%20filed%20a%20defamation%20case%20against%20Gandhi%2C%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20defamed%20the%20%E2%80%98Modi%20community%E2%80%99.%20Gandhi%20has%20maintained%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwill-not-apologise-for-remark-on-modi-surname-as-not-guilty-of-defamation-rahul-gandhi-to-sc%5C%22%3Ethat%20he%20is%20not%20guilty%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20so%20will%20not%20apologise%2C%20while%20also%20arguing%20that%20there%20is%20no%20one%20community%20of%20all%20people%20who%20share%20the%20Modi%20surname.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%2C%20who%20also%20represented%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20courts%2C%20said%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20victory%20for%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20constitution%2C%20democracy%2C%20and%20people%20in%20general%2C%20and%20all%20those%20who%20have%20shown%20courage%20and%20conviction%20in%20the%20face%20of%20an%20all-round%20attack%20on%20the%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20by%20not%20leapfrogging%20from%20the%20first%20appellate%20court%2C%20%5Band%20going%5D%20directly%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Gandhi%20has%20shown%20faith%20in%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20and%20institutions%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20led%20by%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRahul%20Gandhi%20has%20time%20and%20again%20demonstrated%20courage%20and%20conviction.%20His%20actions%2C%20his%20words%20have%20all%20been%20animated%20by%20his%20thinking%2C%20which%20is%20%3Cem%3Edaro%20mat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fear%20not)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singhvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20briefing%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20said%20that%20he%20has%20already%20met%20Lok%20Sabha%20speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20urged%20him%20to%20reinstate%20Gandhi%20as%20the%20MP%20of%20Wayanad%20with%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20same%20speed%20in%20which%20he%20was%20disqualified%20as%20an%20member%20of%20the%20house%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%2C%20which%20was%20published%20on%20August%204%20at%201%3A54%20pm%2C%20has%20been%20republished%20with%20quotes%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20on%20the%20same%20day%20at%206%3A45%20pm.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1691154954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21120741%2FUntitled-design-2-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-stays-rahul-gandhis-conviction-in-defamation-case-questions-lower-court-on-sentence%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22His%20disqualification%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20now%20stands%20in%20abeyance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A90%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-stays-rahul-gandhis-conviction-in-defamation-case-questions-lower-court-on-sentence%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20to%20Expect%20at%20COP28%20UAE%3A%20A%20Global%20Movement%20to%20Fight%20Climate%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EClimate%20action%20requires%20the%20collaboration%20and%20cooperation%20of%20individuals%2C%20communities%2C%20organisations%2C%20and%20governments.%20And%20to%20mitigate%20its%20effects%2C%20we%20need%20to%20shift%20from%20incremental%20steps%20to%20transformational%20progress%20that%20delivers%20for%20everyone%2C%20everywhere.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20exactly%20what%20COP28%20will%20seek%20to%20achieve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20COP%20and%20why%20is%20it%20important%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20is%20the%20supreme%20decision-making%20body%20for%20all%20States%20that%20are%20Parties%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20Framework%20Convention%20on%20Climate%20Change%20(UNFCCC).%20The%20UNFCCC%20came%20into%20force%20on%2021%20March%201994%20with%20the%20aim%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20prevent%20%E2%80%9Cdangerous%E2%80%9D%20human%20interference%20with%20the%20climate%20system%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20COP%20meets%20every%20year%20to%20assess%20the%20progress%20that%20has%20been%20made%20towards%20this.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20meetings%20have%20resulted%20in%20several%20legally%20binding%20international%20agreements%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20including%20the%202015%20Paris%20Agreement%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20limit%20global%20warming%20to%20well%20below%202%20degrees%20Celsius%20above%20pre-industrial%20levels%20and%20pursue%20efforts%20to%20limit%20the%20temperature%20increase%20to%201.5%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECOP28%20UAE%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028th%20COP%20is%20being%20hosted%20by%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20at%20Expo%20City%20Dubai%20between%2030%20November%20and%2012%20December%202023.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20COP%20of%20unity%2C%20solidarity%2C%20and%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECOP28%20will%20see%20the%20first%20Global%20Stocktake%20(GST)%2C%20a%20process%20mandated%20by%20the%20Paris%20Agreement%20to%20evaluate%20advancements%20towards%20its%20objectives.%20It%20is%20against%20this%20backdrop%20that%20COP28%20will%20bring%20everyone%20to%20the%20table%20to%20recalibrate%2C%20raise%20ambitions%20and%20maximise%20the%20opportunities%20of%20the%20clean%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20UAE%20hosted%20the%20annual%20Abu%20Dhabi%20Sustainability%20Week%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286865%2Feasy-steps-to-be-sustainable-at-home-no-plastic-use-save-money-sustainability%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eglobal%20sustainability%3C%2Fa%3E%20event%20established%20in%202008%20to%20accelerate%20sustainable%20economic%20development%20and%20facilitate%20partnerships%20to%20enable%20the%20energy%20transition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20XX%20edition%20of%20ADSW%20drove%20momentum%20between%20COP27%20and%20COP28%2C%20enabling%20impactful%20and%20continuous%20dialogue%20between%20key%20stakeholders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UAE%20was%20the%20first%20country%20in%20the%20region%20to%20announce%20its%20commitment%20to%20Net%20Zero%20and%20has%20a%20proud%20track%20record%20of%20investing%20in%20the%20energy%20transition.%20This%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20evolution%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F271708%2Fstartup-innovation-convert-renewable-energy-water-uravu-labs-bengaluru-engineer%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenewable%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%20powerhouse%2C%20Masdar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20Climate%20Leadership%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMasdar%20was%20established%20in%202006%20as%20part%20of%20the%20UAE%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20vision%20to%20diversify%20its%20economy%20and%20bring%20about%20a%20cycle%20of%20growth%20and%20innovation.%20His%20Excellency%20Dr%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%2C%20the%20COP%20President%20Designate%2C%20is%20Masdar%E2%80%99s%20founding%20CEO%20and%20current%20Chairman.%20Under%20his%20leadership%2C%20the%20company%20has%20grown%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20investors%20in%20renewable%20energy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Masdar%20has%20a%20combined%20investment%20portfolio%20valued%20at%20%2430bn.%20It%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20climate%20innovation%2C%20operating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F287058%2Frenewable-energy-map-india-wind-power-plants-project-largest-solar-park-environment-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20renewable%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20improving%20lives%20in%20over%2040%20countries%20across%206%20continents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EH.E.%20Dr%20Sultan%20Al%20Jaber%20brings%20over%2020%20years%20of%20industry%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20to%20the%20role%20of%20COP%20President-Designate%20and%20is%20uniquely%20positioned%20to%20drive%20critical%20negotiations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20one%20of%20the%20UAE%E2%80%99s%20preeminent%20climate%20champions%2C%20Dr%20Sultan%20has%20outlined%20his%20plans%20to%20deliver%20a%20COP%20for%20all%2C%20underpinned%20by%20the%20belief%20that%20everyone%20must%20be%20on%20board%20in%20order%20to%20accelerate%20progress.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2013%20days%2080%2C000%20participants%2C%20including%20140%20heads%20of%20state%20and%20government%20will%20meet%20in%20the%20UAE%20to%20reduce%20emissions%2C%20protect%20biodiversity%2C%20and%20support%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288116%2Fwhat-antarcticas-40c-weather-iceberg-graveyard-taught-me-about-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffected%20by%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20know%20we%20aren%E2%80%99t%20moving%20fast%20enough%2C%20but%20we%20also%20know%20that%20we%20have%20the%20power%20to%20achieve%20a%20more%20sustainable%20and%20prosperous%20future%2C%20if%20we%20act%20in%20solidarity.%20COP-28%20will%20be%20remembered%20for%20uniting%20everyone%20in%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20drafted%20in%20collaboration%20with%20Masdar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fprocess%2Fbodies%2Fsupreme-bodies%2Fconference-of-the-parties-cop%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUnited%20Nations%20Cl%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Funfccc.int%2Fprocess%2Fbodies%2Fsupreme-b