an%20old%20one%2C%20not%20especially%20architecturally%20significant%2C%20but%20one%20that%20has%20existed%20in%20that%20spot%20for%20a%20long%20time%20though%20clearly%20refurbished%20and%20modernised.%20Also%2C%20one%20that%20is%20evidently%20in%20use%20and%2C%20according%20to%20the%20estate%20agent%2C%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnuisance%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20but%20only%20on%20Fridays%2C%20he%20hastened%20to%20add%2C%20and%20also%20%E2%80%9Cthey%E2%80%9D%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20any%20loudspeakers%20for%20%E2%80%9Ctheir%20%3Cem%3Eajaan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20However%2C%20to%20compound%20matters%2C%20every%20floor%20in%20that%20three-storey%20apartment%20block%20happened%20to%20be%20occupied%2Fowned%20by%20a%20Muslim%20family.%20After%20several%20visits%2C%20I%20eventually%20chickened%20out%20from%20buying%20that%20perfectly%20lovely%20apartment%20in%20a%20perfectly%20lovely%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20giant%2C%20invisible%20yet%20perfectly%20legible%20%E2%80%98X%E2%80%99%20marked%20on%20that%20building.%20The%20proximity%20to%20the%20mosque%2C%20and%20the%20presence%20of%20Muslim%20homeowners%20on%20every%20floor%20of%20that%20house%20in%20an%20otherwise%20entirely%20non-Muslim%20neighbourhood%2C%20brought%20visions%20of%20Ahmadabad%2C%20of%20the%20Gulbarg%20Society%2C%20of%20the%20brutal%20killing%20of%20Congress%20MP%20Ehsan%20Jafri%20and%20at%20least%2035%20others%20inside%20that%20ill-fated%20housing%20society.%20Well-meaning%2C%20liberal%20friends%20made%20me%20feel%20small%20and%20silly%20for%20my%20chicken%20heartedness.%20%E2%80%98Oh%20come%2C%20on!%E2%80%99%20they%20chided%2C%20%E2%80%98That%20was%20Gujarat!%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20happen%20in%20Delhi.%E2%80%99%20Or%2C%20%E2%80%98That%20was%20a%20long%20time%20ago!%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20happen%20now!%E2%80%99%20(Though%2C%20if%20anything%2C%20recent%20events%20in%20Gurgaon%2021%20years%20later%20prove%20otherwise.)%20The%20rational%20ones%20rationalised%2C%20%E2%80%98Gulbarg%20was%20in%20Chamanpura%2C%20a%20Muslim-dominated%20neighboured%3B%20this%20is%20a%20safe%20neighbourhood.%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20happen%20here.%E2%80%99%20And%20worse%20still%2C%20there%20was%20the%20shaming%3A%20%E2%80%98You%20too%3F%20You%20with%20all%20your%20privileges%3F%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20think%20like%20this!%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram's%20Badshahpur%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fi-was-scared-didnt-take-a-chance-muslim-workers-flee-after-violence-in-gurugrams-badshahpur%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20Was%20Scared%2C%20Didn%E2%80%99t%20Take%20a%20Chance%E2%80%99%3A%20Muslim%20Workers%20Flee%20After%20Violence%20in%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Badshahpur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20with%20all%20my%20privileges%20%E2%80%93%20of%20education%2C%20of%20class%2C%20of%20having%20friends%20in%20%E2%80%98high%20places%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20I%20feel%20scared%2C%20more%20scared%20than%20I%20have%20ever%20been%20in%20my%20entire%20life.%20I%20am%2060%20years%20old%20and%20confess%20to%20a%20crushing%20fear%2C%20one%20that%20weighs%20my%20chest%20with%20an%20inexorable%20weight%20and%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20breathe%20sometimes.%20I%20must%20also%20confess%20to%20an%20almost%20persistent%20depression%2C%20like%20a%20low-grade%20fever%2C%20over%20the%20past%20many%20months%2C%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20quite%20halt%20the%20daily%20rhythm%20of%20life%3B%20it%20just%20slows%20you%20down%20by%20its%20continuous%2C%20relentless%20presence%2C%20making%20you%20feel%20sad%20and%20empty%20and%20hopeless.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20suspect%20I%20am%20not%20alone%20in%20this.%20I%20feel%20this%20fear%20and%20depression%20among%20a%20great%20many%20Muslims%20in%20urban%20India.%20I%20hear%20it%20in%20their%20silences.%20I%20sense%20it%20in%20their%20steadfast%20refusal%20to%20get%20drawn%20into%20political%20debates.%20I%20notice%20it%20in%20their%20stoicism%20in%20the%20face%20of%20virulent%20hate%20swirling%20about%20in%20school%20and%20college%20WhatsApp%20groups.%20I%20spot%20it%20in%20the%20hastily%20withdrawn%20social%20media%20posts%20drawing%20attention%20to%20some%20recent%20communal%20outrage%20or%20atrocity.%20I%20recognise%20it%20in%20their%20zeal%20to%20distance%20themselves%20from%20instances%20of%20%3Cem%3Eany%3C%2Fem%3E%20sort%20of%20violence%2C%20be%20it%20a%20Muslim%20man%20killing%20his%20Hindu%20girlfriend%20and%20chopping%20her%20into%20pieces%20or%20a%20Muslim%20man%20killing%20his%20non-Muslim%20partner%20in%20a%20business%20dispute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20my%20own%20fear%20and%20despair%2C%20and%20that%20of%20others%20like%20me%2C%20is%20so%20palpable%20and%20pronounced%2C%20what%20of%20those%20Muslims%20who%20are%20doubly%20marginalised%20by%20their%20poverty%20and%20illiteracy%3F%20Or%20vulnerable%20because%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20safeguards%20and%20barriers%2C%20however%20flimsy%2C%20that%20%E2%80%98people%20like%20us%E2%80%99%20have%20in%20our%20gated%20communities%20and%20cushioned%20lives%3F%20What%20of%20those%20who%20live%20on%20the%20edge%20of%20survival%20because%20they%20must%20perforce%20go%20out%20into%20the%20real%20world%20every%20single%20day%20to%20eke%20out%20a%20living%3F%20What%20of%20the%20plumbers%2C%20electricians%2C%20painters%2C%20carpenters%2C%20maids%20and%20sundry%20service%20providers%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20give%20their%20real%2C%20Muslim-sounding%20names%20for%20fear%20they%20will%20not%20be%20hired%3F%20Or%20the%20vegetable%20vendors%20who%20festoon%20their%20carts%20with%20saffron%20flags%20after%20every%20call%20to%20boycott%20small%20Muslim%20businesses%3F%20Or%20the%20biryani%20vendors%2C%20kebab%20sellers%2C%20quilt%20makers%2C%20car%20mechanics%20who%20have%20traditionally%20plied%20these%20trades%20for%20generations%20but%20now%20fear%20for%20their%20lives%3F%20What%20of%20the%20meat%20sellers%20whose%20makeshift%20stalls%20happen%20to%20be%20along%20the%20routes%20taken%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekawariyas%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20What%20of%20the%20imams%20and%20naib%20imams%2C%20often%20from%20the%20poorest%20of%20families%2C%20who%20are%20hired%20by%20Wakf%20boards%20to%20serve%20as%20custodians%20of%20small%2C%20isolated%20mosques%20surrounded%20by%20hostile%20neighbours%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%98look%E2%80%99%20like%20a%20Muslim%20so%2C%20to%20an%20extent%2C%20I%20am%20safe.%20Unless%20called%20out%20to%20chant%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shree%20Ram%E2%80%99%20to%20profess%20my%20Indianness%2C%20I%20am%20largely%20safe.%20But%20what%20of%20my%20name%3F%20How%20can%20I%20camouflage%20that%20on%20a%20railway%20booking%20chart%3F%20Or%20hide%20it%20when%20asked%20to%20provide%20proof%20of%20identity%3F%20While%20my%20first%20name%20can%20afford%20some%20benefit%20of%20doubt%20for%20it%20might%20pass%20as%20a%20Parsi%E2%80%99s%2C%20my%20surname%20is%20a%20dead%20give-away.%20When%20push%20comes%20to%20shove%20in%20the%20New%20India%20that%20is%20Bharat%2C%20not%20even%20speaking%20English%20will%20give%20me%20an%20exit%20pass%20if%20a%20mob%20baying%20for%20Muslim%20blood%20were%20to%20%3Cem%3Egherao%3C%2Fem%3E%20me.%20All%20my%20so-called%20privileges%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20naught%20by%20a%20lumpen%20crowd.%20The%20realisation%20is%20chilling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Muslim%20Life%20in%20India%20Has%20Become%20Dangerously%20Uncertain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmuslim-life-in-india-has-become-dangerously-uncertain%5C%22%3EMuslim%20Life%20in%20India%20Has%20Become%20Dangerously%20Uncertain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20I%20were%20a%20man%3F%20Imagine%2C%2070%20years%20after%20partition%20and%20after%20reading%20all%20the%20gory%20stories%20penned%20by%20Manto%20and%20other%20chr