80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(What%E2%80%99s%20in%20your%20dabba%20today%3F)%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong-time%20neighbours%20and%20friends%20Anshu%20Ahuja%20and%20Renee%20Williams%2C%20too%2C%20find%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabba%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20be%20the%20voice%20of%20their%20dreams.%20In%202018%2C%20they%20started%20Dabba%20Drop%2C%20and%20Anshu%20says%20that%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20starting%20an%20eco-friendly%20delivery%20business%20was%20the%20waste%20that%20gets%20accumulated%20when%20we%20order%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20people%20have%20started%20ordering%20a%20lot%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20arrival%20of%20food%20delivery%20apps.%20After%20having%20that%20food%2C%20we%20end%20up%20with%20a%20bin%20full%20of%20plastic.%20The%20packaging%20is%20very%20wasteful%20and%20greasy.%20You%20can%E2%80%99t%20recycle%20it.%20So%20I%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20better%20way%20to%20order%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20Anshu%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20Mumbai%20with%20a%20Tamilian%20mother%20and%20Punjabi%20father%2C%20food%20was%20a%20big%20part%20of%20her%20life%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20my%20favourite%20food%20when%20we%20would%20go%20out%20to%20eat%20was%20%3Cem%3Epav%20bhaji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20chinese.%20When%20I%E2%80%99d%20get%20home%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20try%20to%20recreate%20those%20dishes.%20This%20way%20I%20could%20continue%20to%20taste%20the%20flavours.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20childhood%20in%20Mumbai%20meant%20that%20Anshu%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabbawalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20have%20been%20serving%20food%20to%20over%202%20lakh%20people%20daily%20since%201890.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20this%20mix%20of%20love%20for%20home-cooked%20food%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Edabbawala%20institution%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20led%20her%20to%20quit%20her%2015-year-long%20career%20as%20a%20TV%20