lps%20the%20women%20get%20early%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%20if%20any%20changes%20are%20needed%20in%20nutrition%2C%20sleep%20cycle%2C%20etc.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20convert%20high-risk%20pregnancies%20into%20low-risk%20ones%20by%20ensuring%20the%20timely%20provision%20of%20medication%20and%20proper%20nutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%2030%20lakh%20mothers%20from%2014%2C328%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20Through%20a%201%2C000-day%20care%20programme%2C%20he%20has%20also%20helped%20at%20least%207%2C320%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20sister%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20to%20lifesaving%20innovation%20for%20rural%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20came%20across%20the%20pregnancy%20healthcare%20gap%20when%20his%20sister%20was%20pregnant%20in%202016.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20career-driven%20woman%20and%20would%20miss%20her%20antenatal%20appointments%20due%20to%20the%20lack%20of%20time.%20Also%2C%20the%20distance%20from%20her%20village%20to%20the%20hospital%20is%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20Madurai%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20informs%20that%20since%202019%2C%20the%20startup%20has%20catered%20to%20more%20than%20three%20lakh%20mothers%20from%2014%2C328%20villages%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Kerala.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-3-1690550200.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiov