20causes%20nutritional%20deficiencies%20among%20them.%20This%20changes%20their%20blood%20glucose%20and%20pressure%2C%20and%20ECG.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20these%20devices%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20problems%20and%20alert%20local%20healthcare%20workers.%20Accordingly%2C%20we%20are%20also%20able%20to%20prescribe%20iron%20supplements%2C%20folic%20acid%20tablets%2C%20and%20other%20nutrition%20supplements%20to%20the%20women.%20I%20can%20monitor%20their%20health%20by%20sitting%20in%20my%20OPD.%20We%20have%20been%20able%20to%20save%20hundreds%20of%20lives%20thanks%20to%20these%20devices.%20They%20have%20a%20huge%20potential%20to%20reduce%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F175789%2Fias-hero-telangana-maternal-mortality-un-sdg-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernal%20mortality%20%3C%2Fa%3Erate%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20claims%20that%20he%20has%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20maternal%20mortality%20by%2010%20percent%20in%20the%20regions%20he%20has%20worked.%20For%20him%2C%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20work%20is%20extremely%20satisfying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20five%20years%20into%20any%20corporate%20job%2C%20the%20work%20is%20pretty%20much%20the%20same.%20I%20chose%20entrepreneurship%20because%20it%20gives%20me%20more%20learning%20opportunities.%20Instead%20of%20working%20in%20a%20big%20Fortune%20500%20company%2C%20this%20work%20gives%20me%20immense%20gratification.%20It%20is%20fulfilling%20to%20see%20we%20are%20able%20to%20save%20lives%20with%20our%20devices%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20shares%20that%20he%20now%20intends%20to%20expand%20their%20services%20in%20North%20and%20Northeast%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofol