apital%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20involved%20thinking%20of%20different%20ways%20to%20manage%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20waste%2C%20which%20led%20her%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20garbage%20dump%20yards%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20were%20facing%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20environmental%20pollution.%20We%20would%20make%20multiple%20visits%20to%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20and%20seeing%20its%20condition%20just%20shook%20me.%20I%20was%20frustrated%20seeing%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20chip%20packets%20there%3B%20the%20amount%20of%20plastic%20waste%20there%20was%20humongous%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhagyashree%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20published%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20has%2078%20lakh%20MT%20of%20waste%20and%20reached%20its%20saturation%20point%20in%202002.%20Yet%2C%20700%20MT%20of%20waste%20is%20dumped%20there%20daily.%20Work%20is%20underway%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20(MCD)%20to%20flatten%20the%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20recycling%20her%20life%20mission%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201328px)%20100vw%2C%201328px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221328%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trash%20being%20separated%20in%20a%20dumpyard%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328.jpeg%201328w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-300x168.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Ftdc-11-min-1690546328-500x280.jpeg%2050