0borrowers.%20They%20are%20asked%20for%20NOCs%20from%20their%20husbands%20or%20fathers%20even%20when%20they%20are%20financially%20independent%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20says%20that%20there%20is%20a%20very%20high%20demand%20for%20loans%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310452%2Fbengaluru-student-financial-independence-portal-for-domestic-workers-finwin-anaya-jethanandani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewomen%20who%20run%20small%20businesse%3C%2Fa%3Es.%20She%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20unlock%20capital%20worth%20billions%20of%20dollars%20for%20these%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20India%20has%20to%20become%20a%20prosperous%20and%20more%20equitable%20country%2C%20she%20needs%20to%20give%20women%20more%20credit.%20These%20loans%20help%20families%20overcome%20poverty.%20We%20will%20help%20as%20many%20women%20as%20possible%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprotium.co.in%2F2023%2F01%2F09%2Fwomen-entrepreneurs-financing-gap%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAs%2520per%25202021%2527s%2520Global%2520Findex%2Cshare%2520against%252015%2525%2520for%2520men.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProtium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Feconomy%2Findicators%2Fwomen-more-credit-conscious-than-men-report%2Farticleshow%2F81389164.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Women%20more%20credit%20conscious%20than%20men%3A%20Report%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Gayatri%20Nayak%20for%20Economic%20Times%2C%20Published%20on%2008%20March%2C%202021%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1